sub_title: Urban Planning and Development, Land Governance for Sustainable Development
summary:
I am an Urbanist, specialized in Urban Land Governance for sustainable development. I intend to comprehend and tackle the manifold dynamics of global sustainability and urbanization challenges through inclusive socio-economic and environmental practices. My interest and area of competence are sustainable techniques, land-use planning, ecosystem services, resilient infrastructure development, policy research, and data analysis. I aspire to grow and pursue opportunities in the field of sustainable urban development through policy research, resilient climate change adaptation, development of knowledge products, and exploring innovative methods, to make
cities work.
